com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.builder
Interface IGeospatialPropertyValueBuilder

public interface IGeospatialPropertyValueBuilder

A builder for creating a ComplexPropertyValue that represents a geospatial value in the Analysis Repository. To use the builder, start by getting and using the sub-builders for the different parts of the geospatial value. Then, call build() to validate, create, and return the ComplexPropertyValue.

Since:
4.0
